high_descs: Head left down the corridor, take the first turn on the left, walk straight, take a turn left just before an apple in front of you, and get to a box on the floor.
Pick up the apple from the box.
Turn around, walk straight to the wall, then right until you reach a cross section where you go left and then to the upper right corner of the room where you can see the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave, heat it up for a while, then take the apple out.
Leave the room and go down the same path in the corridor to the place where you got the apple, but this time go right to the bathroom sink.
Put the apple on the bathroom sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the heated-up apple on the sink in the bathroom.
